HTTPServer:
	Handle requests for join/create/leave group
	Handle requests for uploading file
Instructions:
	- join/create group: http://localhost:8080/join, http://SERVERIP/create, users can join and create groups
	- leave group: curl -i -d "clientip=192.168.0.107&groupid=0" localhost:8080/leave
	- upload file: http://localhost:8080/upload 